4297, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "jihyxjhy", "last_touched": 1774597643, "title": "这就是国产大模型！混元！混尼玛呢！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201399", "created": 1774520530, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://i.imgur.com/bW0q0uo.png)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bW0q0uo.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1774520530, "replies": 102, "id": 1201399}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10433, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2237, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 641913, "username": "Exxfire", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Exxfire", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "重庆", "tagline": "", "bio": "Github: https://github.com/Exxfire", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d0c05e7c27c838082240f375e003f5ec?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d0c05e7c27c838082240f375e003f5ec?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d0c05e7c27c838082240f375e003f5ec?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1691200976, "last_modified": 1739413444, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ilovebaicai", "last_touched": 1774597956, "title": "昨晚买了人生中的第一套房", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1201611", "created": 1774594066, "deleted": 0, "content": "97 年人，今年 29 岁了，昨晚 10 点多签下了合同，在重庆主城区买了人生中的第一套房。\r\n房子建面 93 平米多一点，小三室，一个卫生间，朝南，安静，高层，离地铁步行 10 分钟，总价 48.5 个, 除了客厅略小，其它都挺满意，首付 20.5 个，贷款 28 个，给中介付了 6000 。\r\n公司不稳定，但是有女朋友和家人的支持，贷款数额不算很多，7 点看房，聊了会果断选择拿下。\r\n从 19 年元旦来到重庆，已经过去了这么多年，总算要在这个城市有一个自己的家了。\r\n特发此贴，纪念一下人生的到目前为止的最大一笔大宗交易。", "content_rendered": "<p>97 年人，今年 29 岁了，昨晚 10 点多签下了合同，在重庆主城区买了人生中的第一套房。\n房子建面 93 平米多一点，小三室，一个卫生间，朝南，安静，高层，离地铁步行 10 分钟，总价 48.5 个, 除了客厅略小，其它都挺满意，首付 20.5 个，贷款 28 个，给中介付了 6000 。\n公司不稳定，但是有女朋友和家人的支持，贷款数额不算很多，7 点看房，聊了会果断选择拿下。\n从 19 年元旦来到重庆，已经过去了这么多年，总算要在这个城市有一个自己的家了。\n特发此贴，纪念一下人生的到目前为止的最大一笔大宗交易。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1774594066, "replies": 97, "id": 1201611}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_large.png?m=1650095204", "name": "nodejs", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_normal.png?m=1650095204", "title": "Node.js", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nodejs", "topics": 2600, "footer": "", "header": "Node.js is a platform built on <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/v8/\" target=\"_blank\">Chrome's JavaScript runtime</a> for easily building fast, scalable network applications.", "title_alternative": "Node.js", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_mini.png?m=1650095204", "stars": 2939, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 436, "parent_node_name": "js"}, "member": {"id": 40195, "username": "BeijingBaby", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/BeijingBaby", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_mini.png?m=1763689815", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_normal.png?m=1763689815", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_large.png?m=1763689815", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_xlarge.png?m=1763689815", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_xxlarge.png?m=1763689815", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_xxxlarge.png?m=1763689815", "created": 1370421009, "last_modified": 1763689815, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "CosmoLau", "last_touched": 1774597980, "title": "2026 年， node 写后端你用的 nestjs, fastify, honojs 还是其他？", 